# ── Signing & keystore artefacts (defense in depth) ───────
# The Play Store keystore is decoded transiently in CI (.github/workflows/play-store.yml)
# and rm'd in `if: always()`, but a workflow interrupted between decode and rm could
# leak it via failure artifacts. These patterns also block accidental `git add -A`
# after running release tooling locally.
**/*.keystore
**/*.jks
**/google-services.json
**/Secrets.xcconfig
**/*.p12
**/*.mobileprovision
# Exception: React Native debug keystore is the well-known shared dev key,
# safe to track and required for RN Android dev builds.
!samples/react-native-demo/android/app/debug.keystore

